{
  "stem": "14060.9",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there we were greeted that unless we turn around right away-- don't forget, it was a private group-- and go back to Linz, they're going to arrest us and put us into a Nazi camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We said, thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we all nicely got back to Linz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there we were informed, no way can we get across unless we go into a DP camp from where they will organize it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now, we had a-- an extremely strong antagonism to be put under control of a camp-- of any control.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That was-- that was the worst thing anybody could suggest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But after a day or two consultation amongst ourself-- and we were sitting around at the railway station-- we decided we had no option.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We got into that camp, and literally within a few days, they put together a transport-- perfectly normal-- and we were sent south to Graz, which was English zone.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And from there the train was turned around and went up to Wiener Neustadt, which is between Vienna and where I come from.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that's where we got off the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That's where I met the Russian soldiers for the first time in my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we thought we'd just get on the next train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We asked which way the train is going, and the next thing [LAUGHS] he pointed the machine gun at us and in some very rude Russian words, which later on I knew to understand, said that unless we come off, he shoots us on the spot.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyway, we understood the message.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We got off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "A half an hour later, we got onto another train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I was back within an hour in our town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And quickly news spread that I arrived.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
